<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.230187>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 7. Pedoniphis persicus gen. nov, sp. nov., female. 1. Dorsal idiosoma; 2. Ventral idiosoma; 3. Subcapitulum; 4. Epistome; 5. Chelicera; 6. Epigynal shield, a variant form with genital setae off the shield; 7. Femur II. Figs 6 and 7 not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/230187/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

